eplyTime":"2017-12-14T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不妨數下有幾多件垃圾<del>有</del><span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>殘體字</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}